The '''Governor of Caluula''' was a [[Gender/Legends|female]] [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] [[Governor/Legends|governor]] of [[Caluula/Legends|Caluula]] during the end of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. In [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]] after the [[Battle of Caluula]], she made a deal with the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] that would allow them to occupy Caluula in exchange for not using [[Yorik-Kul|surge-coral]] and allowing scientists onworld to witness the [[Nocturne of the Winged-Stars]]. The decision made her extremely disliked among the populace, and she retreated behind her walled headquarters. However, in actuality she agreed to the peaceful occupation in order to provide a base for the testing of the [[Alpha Red (pathogen)|Alpha Red]] virus.

